{"type": "article", "id": 21797, "title": "Entryway Collection by Grovemade", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-03T08:14:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 62, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122304DN7BVdZ58p4IAnKE.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一组墙面小工具，包括挂钩、收纳盒、盆景和镜子。它们都使用了胡桃木，里面嵌有金属支撑，使得这组物件拥有木头的简洁和质感，也有助于统一风格。挂钩是一块带斜面的实体，外面钉了一层植鞣皮，依靠错开的角度来挂物品。收纳盒盆景的“围栏”都保持了一个倾斜的角度，增加了墙面的活力。挂钩售价 39 美元，<a href=\"http://grovemade.com/collections/entryway-collection\">这里是购买链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122301eXyTazU7qEQ5NWKP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"medium-insert-active com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071223026eQsDfWLhUdCZv5u.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.68666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122302ACsmB0RTSYUxOLNh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122302FSfmqyDrHlEja0Jk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.51666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122303BR0dV9m6taWZsAeU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}